[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":273},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fnext-hide-disqus-on-tags-categories\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fnext-hide-disqus-on-tags-categories\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fnext-hide-disqus-on-tags-categories\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fnext-hide-disqus-on-tags-categories\u002F":250,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fnext-hide-disqus-on-tags-categories\u002F":259},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20190516\u002F2710757554\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":234,"date":235,"description":19,"extension":236,"lang":237,"meta":238,"navigation":239,"path":240,"readingMinutes":241,"seo":242,"standalone":243,"stem":244,"tags":245,"tldr":247,"updated":235,"url":248,"__hash__":249},"content\u002Fen\u002FHexo\u002Fnext-hide-disqus-on-tags-categories.md","Hide Disqus on NexT Category and Tag Pages","4557570172",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":225},"minimark",[11,16,20,24,29,39,43,48,52,60,67,74,85,90,93,128,133,136,139,144,147,152,155,160,164,167,170,188,197,200,203,208,211,221],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"NexT is a great theme, but a few quirks are weird — like Disqus comments showing up on the tags and categories pages. Here's how to hide them.",[12,21,23],{"id":22},"environment-for-this-post","Environment for this post",[25,26,28],"h3",{"id":27},"hexo-version","Hexo version",[30,31,32,36],"ul",{},[33,34,35],"li",{},"hexo: 3.8.0",[33,37,38],{},"hexo-cli: 2.0.0",[25,40,42],{"id":41},"next-version","NexT version",[30,44,45],{},[33,46,47],{},"NexT: 7.1.0",[12,49,51],{"id":50},"edit-the-template","Edit the template",[17,53,54,55,59],{},"Since we're using NexT, edit the template file (",[56,57,58],"code",{},"\\themes\\hexo-theme-next-master\\layout\\_layout.swig",").",[17,61,62,63,66],{},"Tag and category pages use the same template as articles, so the file to edit is ",[56,64,65],{},"_layout.swig",".",[17,68,69],{},[70,71],"img",{"alt":72,"src":73},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FPZSwK3c.png",[17,75,76,77,80,81,84],{},"Search for ",[56,78,79],{},"comments.swig"," — you'll find a line like ",[56,82,83],{},"{% include '_partials\u002Fcomments.swig' %}",". That's where the comments get included.",[17,86,87],{},[70,88],{"alt":72,"src":89},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FBUatGte.png",[17,91,92],{},"Wrap that include in a conditional:",[94,95,100],"pre",{"className":96,"code":97,"language":98,"meta":99,"style":99},"language-swig shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{% set page_type = page.type === 'tags' || page.type === 'categories' %}\n  \u003Cdiv style=\"{%if page_type %} visibility:hidden; height:0px;{% endif %}\">\n  {% include '_partials\u002Fcomments.swig' %}\n  \u003C\u002Fdiv>\n","swig","",[56,101,102,110,116,122],{"__ignoreMap":99},[103,104,107],"span",{"class":105,"line":106},"line",1,[103,108,109],{},"{% set page_type = page.type === 'tags' || page.type === 'categories' %}\n",[103,111,113],{"class":105,"line":112},2,[103,114,115],{},"  \u003Cdiv style=\"{%if page_type %} visibility:hidden; height:0px;{% endif %}\">\n",[103,117,119],{"class":105,"line":118},3,[103,120,121],{},"  {% include '_partials\u002Fcomments.swig' %}\n",[103,123,125],{"class":105,"line":124},4,[103,126,127],{},"  \u003C\u002Fdiv>\n",[17,129,130],{},[70,131],{"alt":72,"src":132},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F0TStEMK.png",[17,134,135],{},"Save, restart, and check whether the tag and category pages still show comments.",[17,137,138],{},"tags:",[17,140,141],{},[70,142],{"alt":72,"src":143},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fww8dOWI.png",[17,145,146],{},"categories:",[17,148,149],{},[70,150],{"alt":72,"src":151},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FaAiVa3q.png",[17,153,154],{},"article page:",[17,156,157],{},[70,158],{"alt":72,"src":159},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FqCYebRu.png",[12,161,163],{"id":162},"extra","Extra",[17,165,166],{},"While writing this post, I hit a landmine. Hexo uses the swig template engine, so when I wrote swig syntax inside the article, it kept erroring out. Thankfully the official docs cover this.",[17,168,169],{},"From the official docs:",[171,172,173],"blockquote",{},[17,174,175,176,179,180,183,184,187],{},"Hexo uses Nunjucks to render posts (older versions used Swig — the syntax is similar). If the content includes ",[56,177,178],{},"{{ }}"," or ",[56,181,182],{},"{% %}",", it might throw parsing errors. Wrap them in a ",[56,185,186],{},"raw"," tag to avoid issues.",[17,189,190],{},[191,192,196],"a",{"href":193,"rel":194},"https:\u002F\u002Fhexo.io\u002Fdocs\u002Ftroubleshooting.html",[195],"nofollow","Escape content",[17,198,199],{},"5\u002F18 update — landmine notes:",[17,201,202],{},"Originally I wrote it this way:",[17,204,205],{},[70,206],{"alt":72,"src":207},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fh1N8vCY.png",[17,209,210],{},"But this approach throws errors, so the approach in that screenshot doesn't work.",[17,212,213,216,217,220],{},[56,214,215],{},"display:none"," also throws warnings. So using ",[56,218,219],{},"visibility:hidden; height:0px;"," is the safest.",[222,223,224],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":99,"searchDepth":112,"depth":112,"links":226},[227,228,232,233],{"id":14,"depth":112,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":112,"text":23,"children":229},[230,231],{"id":27,"depth":118,"text":28},{"id":41,"depth":118,"text":42},{"id":50,"depth":112,"text":51},{"id":16